headline: Winged Keel Group Names Jacob Boston as Managing Director, Marketing and Communications
summary: NEW YORK, September 29, 2025--Winged Keel Group "Winged Keel" is pleased to announce the addition of Jacob Boston as Managing Director, Marketing and Communications. In this newly created role, Jacob will oversee the strategic direction and execution of Winged Keel Group’s marketing and communications platform. headline: NFP Enhances Its Cross-Border Portfolio, Launches Conduzco Seguros and Establishes Strategic Partnership With Quálitas
summary: NFP, an Aon company and leading property and casualty (P&C) broker, benefits consultant, wealth manager and retirement plan advisor, today launched Conduzco Seguros, a Spanish-language, online-based Mexican auto insurance solution for drivers crossing the border into Mexico. Developed in partnership with Quálitas Compañía de Seguros (Quálitas), a leading Mexican insurance company, the offering is tailored to the needs of the U.S. Spanish-speaking market. summary: Aon recently expanded its analytics services with the enhanced TPI Portfolio, aiming to help insurers improve risk assessment and underwriting decisions, and appointed Leon Walker as EMEA captives leader to drive strategy and growth across the region. headline: Tommy Fleetwood of Team Europe wins Nicklaus-Jacklin Award presented by Aon at 45th Ryder Cup
summary: Today, Tommy Fleetwood of Team Europe has been named the recipient of the Nicklaus-Jacklin Award presented by Aon following the conclusion of the 45th Ryder Cup at Bethpage Black in New York.
